<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Agnes Njoroge - AI & ML Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #24292e;
            background-color: #fafbfc;
        }
        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #24292e;
        }
        h1 {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #0366d6;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #586069;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 35px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e1e4e8;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        a {
            color: #0366d6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .btn-resume {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0366d6;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .btn-resume:hover {
            background-color: #0255b3;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
        }
        .skills-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .skills-category h4 {
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
            color: #0366d6;
        }
        .skills-category p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .project-card {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e1e4e8;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .project-card h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 60px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e1e4e8;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #586069;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Agnes Njoroge</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">AI Student & Aspiring Machine Learning Engineer</p>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>I'm a student currently studying <strong>Artificial Intelligence</strong>. I am deeply interested in <strong>Machine Learning</strong>, data analysis, and building intelligent systems that can extract insights from complex datasets and solve real-world problems.</p>
        <!-- Change the # to your actual Google Drive or Dropbox resume link later -->
        <a href="#" class="btn-resume" target="_blank">📄 View My Resume</a>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Skills & Tools</h2>
        <div class="skills-container">
            <div class="skills-category">
                <h4>Languages</h4>
                <p>Python, SQL, HTML/CSS</p>
            </div>
            <div class="skills-category">
                <h4>AI & ML Libraries</h4>
                <p>Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-Learn</p>
            </div>
            <div class="skills-category">
                <h4>Tools & Platforms</h4>
                <p>Git, GitHub, Jupyter Notebooks, Google Colab</p>
            </div>
            <div class="skills-category">
                <h4>Core Concepts</h4>
                <p>Data Cleaning, Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA), Predictive Modeling</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3><a href="#" target="_blank">Predictive Modeling Project</a></h3>
            <p>A machine learning project built with Python and Scikit-Learn to analyze a dataset and predict outcomes. Cleaned data, performed EDA, and trained a regression/classification model.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
            <h3><a href="#" target="_blank">Personal Portfolio</a></h3>
            <p>This very website! Built using HTML and CSS to showcase my skills, AI/ML learning journey, and projects.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
        <p>Feel free to reach out or check out my work across the web:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/your-username" target="_blank">@your-username</a></li>
            <li><strong>LinkedIn:</strong> <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/agnes-njoroge" target="_blank">Agnes Njoroge</a></li>
            <!-- Optional profiles common in ML -->
            <li><strong>Kaggle:</strong> <a href="https://kaggle.com/your-username" target="_blank">Kaggle Profile</a></li> 
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com">your.email@example.com</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2026 Agnes Njoroge. Built with HTML & CSS.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
